Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.69,0:00:10.27,Default,Alarm,0000,0000,0000,,Ju{\fscx125}~{\r}tro{\fscx125}~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.27,0:00:11.90,Default,Alarm,0000,0000,0000,,Jutro{\fscx125}~{\r}je{\fscx125}~
